Empire 5 is a Rust rewrite of Wolfpack Empire 4.4.1.  All game logic,
data structures, and protocol design derive from the work of the original
Empire contributors listed below.  Empire 5 inherits the GNU General
Public License v3 from the upstream project; see COPYING for the full
license text.

---

